---
title: Sweet Chilli Fritters & Haloumi Stack with Kumara Toss
description: These juicy, sweet and salty fritters are the perfect marriage of flavours and easy cooking techniques. Each fritter is packed with veggies, and is stacked with tasty haloumi and sweet chilli sauce to add plenty of cheesy goodness!
